query.sql:
select
  CASE_ID,
  PROC_DATE,
  COLLISION_DATE,
  COLLISION_TIME,
  PRIMARY_RD,
  WEATHER_1,
  NUMBER_KILLED,
  NUMBER_INJURED,
  PARTY_COUNT,
  ALCOHOL_INVOLVED,
  LATITUDE,
  LONGITUDE
from
  CHP_20
where
  LATITUDE is not null
  and LONGITUDE is not null
  and NUMBER_KILLED > 0
  and ALCOHOL_INVOLVED = 'Y'
order by
  NUMBER_KILLED desc
